name: Chay_Lelando
content:
Chay Lelando, the "Millennium Falcon Man", was a Human male.
Leland Chee portrayed this character for the trailer associated with the launch of the Star Wars: Millennium Falcon: A 3-D Owner's Guide. In a StarWars.com article about Leland Chee's Holocron continuity database, Chay Lelando's entry was used to showcase the database.
